				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ffb3" distance="0" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1176" y="728" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="13" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#b8b8b8" width="74" height="18" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.6">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="13" fontWeight="bold" color="#b8b8b8">× 10.6</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ccff" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="762" width="502" height="154" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">初始为「刚性」聚合状态，首次分裂倒计时为<span color="#ffdfbf">35s</span><span>，若分裂期间击败8个及以上孢子，则会使曼陀草进入「脆性」聚合状态，使分裂倒计时延长至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">44s</span><span>，否则依旧处于「刚性」状态，分裂倒计时延长至为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">38s</span><span>。<br/>处于「刚性」状态时，抗打断0.12。<br/>分裂倒计时可被</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>与</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>元素攻击加速，根据其元素量扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">n*1s</span><span>或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.15s</span><span>。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>各分裂倒计时延长3s，对应上述变为38s、41s、47s；分裂倒计时加速数值变化，现根据其元素量扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">n*0.5s</span><span>或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.5s</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="954" width="497" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">分裂倒计时结束后分裂为10个孢子，持续17s，孢子为<span color="#ffdfbf">曼陀草10%生命值</span><span>。对孢子造成伤害时，也会对曼陀草造成伤害。若低于</span><span color="#ffebbf">20%生命值</span><span>则根据剩余生命分裂对应数量的孢子(2%/个)；低于</span><span color="#ffebbf">2%生命值</span><span>则不再分裂。</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>分裂状态延长5s，即22s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<Rect x="576" y="32" width="768" height="768" alpha="1" d:userLabel="固定矩形" visible="false" blendMode="normal" radiusX="0" radiusY="0">
			<fill>
				<SolidColor color="#ffffff"/>
			</fill>
		</Rect>
