		<RichText x="1538" y="320" width="444" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">曼陀草初始处于「刚性」聚合状态，首次<span textDecoration="underline">分裂倒计时</span><span>为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">38s</span><span>，后续为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">41s</span><span>；倒计时结束后，在9-12m范围内分裂为10个</span><span textDecoration="underline">孢子</span><span>，持续</span><span color="#ffdfbf">22s</span><span>；之后恢复。若期间击败8个及以上孢子，则会使曼陀草恢复后退出「刚性」状态，并使分裂倒计时延长至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">47s</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
